here the registration and breakfast take place on the first day. For other details on transportation, see also &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/venue/getting-around-aarhus&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Getting Around in Aarhus&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/venue/conference-dinner#conference-dinner-transport&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Conference Dinner Transport&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
